<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6802700>
    dc:description "Figs 1-9: Male genital segment, sternite of the same and aedeadus (1-3) of Neoxantholinus thailandicus nov.sp. Tergite and sternite of the male genital segment and aedeagus (4-6) of Metolinus squamifer nov.sp. Tergite and sternite of the male genital segment and aedeagus (7-9) of Mahavana eximia nov.sp. (m= membranous part) (scale bar: 0.1 mm)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/6802700/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

